Yesterday, A bag with an bran-new phone was stolen.
Someone stole the bag in the cafeteria at school. 
The time will be set from 1 p.m to 2 p.m
The police caught three people they think might have done it. 
Right now, the three persons who are regarded as suspects are asked to write their alibi within 10 sentences. 
After writing their alibi, police (the other students) will ask them 5 questions. 
The suspects say they can prove they didn't do the robbery and they insist they are innocent.
